'''La-La Land'''-  a place occasionally referred to in the expression "Drifting into La-La Land", or, "He is in La-La Land."  Both refer to not paying attention.

La-La land means a place where a person's state of mind is characterized by unrealistic anticipations and lack of sincerity. Because of its eccentricities, Los Angeles; in other words, LA has been given this nick name of "la-la land". This expression pokes fun at the alleged weirdness of the city's inhabitants. The city's chaotic societal conditions and the inadvertent people make them seem to be existing in La-La Land (A land of carelessness, which is renowned for its frivolous activities).